bcid.Renderer
Interface RendererInterface

All Known Implementing Classes:
HTMLTableRenderer, JSONRenderer, RDFRenderer, RedirectRenderer, Renderer, TextRenderer
public interface RendererInterface

rendererInterface defines an interface for working with rendered identifiers . Can enter an object, printMetadata, and leave. These methods are meant to populate a class level variable in the Renderer

Method Summary

          Enter the genericIdentifier and render any information before looking at metadata

          Leave the object and print any relevant closing information
 void printMetadata()
          Print an identifier's metadata
 boolean validIdentifier()
          Need to always check the identifier and provide a consistent method for returning error messages if it is bad.
